name: Mooi Indo #1
description:
Sometimes I love to shoot landscapes. I rarely post, show, or sell them on any platform. I am always scared that it will ruin people's vision of my work. But as NFT is decentralized market, I embrace my admiration of landscape. Through Mooi Indo series, I will published more of landscape photos.
Let's be ordinary!

This photo was taken in 2020, around Sayang Heulang, West Java, Indonesia
